---
title: Cheesy Beef & Kidney Bean Enchiladas  with Sour Cream & Radish Salad
description: Enchiladas – what could be more fun? Take one part tasty beans and veg, one part soft tortillas and one part saucy beef, then combine them
and top the whole thing with melty cheesy goodness. With a fresh radish salad, this is a sure-fire winner.
